FBIS4-62797 "drsov095_b_94016" FBIS-SOV-94-095 Daily Report 14 May 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Political & Social Issues Pamfilova Invited To Head Newly Formed Social Policy Body Pamfilova Invited To Head Newly Formed Social Policy Body MK1405122094 Moscow SEGODNYA in Russian 14 May 94 p 1 MK1405122094 Moscow SEGODNYA Russian BFN [Unattributed report: "A Social Policy Council Will Be Established"] [Text] According to information from reliable sources, a decision has effectively been made to create a Social Policy Council within the Russian Federation presidential administration, the leadership of which has been offered to Ella Pamfilova, former [social welfare] minister and currently a State Duma deputy.
